<br>
You do need to have people that are willing to do exactly as their told, and if they make a mistake to take one for team and die for it.<br>
<br>
Get a few groups of your friends, invis up, zone in, turn left, run down hill and wait for mobs to start aggroing.  Kill them and keep killing them until you have to pull to get them to your camp.<br>
<br>
That is how simple breaking fear is.  The biggest problem you will face is the people who come on the raid. <p>----------
